</div><big> 
<p>If you want ANVILL to work well in any situation, use:</p>
<p><img class="emoji" draggable="false" alt="✅" src="../assets/svg/twemoji/2705.svg"> <strong>Google Chrome</strong><br>
<img class="emoji" draggable="false" alt="✅" src="../assets/svg/twemoji/2705.svg"> <strong>Mozilla Firefox</strong>*<br>
<img class="emoji" draggable="false" alt="✅" src="../assets/svg/twemoji/2705.svg"> <strong>Microsoft Edge</strong>*<br>
*(note: Firefox and Edge work well with everything <em>except</em> &quot;Speak the Words&quot; activities which use Speech Recognition software requiring Chrome)</p>
<p>Other browsers are incompatible with the rich variety of ANVILL activities.</p>
<p>Thus, ANVILL does not currently support:</p>
<p><img class="emoji" draggable="false" alt="❌" src="../assets/svg/twemoji/274c.svg"><strong>Apple Safari</strong></p>
<h1 id="download-chrome-for-free" class="toc-header"><a class="toc-anchor" href="browser#download-chrome-for-free">¶</a> Download Chrome for Free</h1>
<p>Click here to <a href="https://www.google.com/chrome/?brand=CHBD&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwq832BRA5EiwACvCWsSVEZ_szcU94T1yabTUEHH3OvRmvSyxKXxXwXS4ez35gChoeTB_OlBoCmA4QAvD_BwE&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds" class="is-external-link">download Chrome for free</a> on Windows, Linux, or Mac.</p>
